div1.p: Territory of Washington County of King} SS

H.N.H. Harris, special Constable, do truly return to the Hon Roger S. Greene, Cheif Justice of the Territory of Washington and Judge of the 3rd District of said territory, that before the foregoing to in of the annexed writ of Habeas Corpus, that said C.W. Hitchingson, was arrested at Port Hakeley, Kitsah County, in said Territory, by a deputy, sheriff of said Kitsah County, said by said deputy sheriff committed to my custody to be surveyed to Pierce County in said Territory, under and by virtue of a cutain warrant of arrest a true copy of which is here to annxed the original of which I havewith produce; nonetheles I have
the body of the said C.N. Hutchinson before you as I am Commanded
Subscribed and sworn to before me this 12th day of November 1885,
